<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hills University of Crypto</title>
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #f2a900; --dark: #1a1a1a; --light: #ffffff; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; margin: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: var(--dark); }
        header { background: var(--dark); color: var(--primary); padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary); }
        .ticker { background: #eee; padding: 10px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        .hero { text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px; background: white; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-top: 5px solid var(--primary); }
        .btn { background: var(--primary); color: var(--dark); padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>🏛️ Hills University of Crypto</h1>
    <p>Empowering the next generation of Blockchain Experts</p>
</header>

<div class="ticker">
    <script src="https://widgets.coingecko.com/coingecko-coin-price-marquee-widget.js"></script>
    <coingecko-coin-price-marquee-widget  coin-ids="bitcoin,ethereum,ripple,binancecoin,cardano" currency="usd" background-color="#eeeeee" locale="en"></coingecko-coin-price-marquee-widget>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
        <h2>Master the Future of Money</h2>
        <p>Access curated materials, market insights, and statistical analysis on the world of Digital Assets.</p>
        <a href="#materials" class="btn">Explore Materials</a>
    </div>
<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518546305927-5a555bb7020d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" 
         alt="Crypto Workspace" 
         style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
</div>
    <h2 id="materials">Learning Modules</h2>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Fundamentals</h3>
            <p>What is Bitcoin? Learn the basics of Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT).</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Get PDF</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Market Analysis</h3>
            <p>Using Statistics to understand crypto trends and volatility.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">View Charts</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Smart Contracts</h3>
            <p>Introduction to Ethereum and decentralized applications (dApps).</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Join Lab</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: #888;">
    <p>&copy; 2026 Hills University of Crypto | Built by Jonathan Ochichi</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>



